
Working with Drives
	
	Format
	
	> format d:
	> format d: /q  
		(quick format)
	
	
	Patition
	
	> diskpart
	> list disk
	> select disk 6
	> list partition
	> select partition 0
	> delete partition 
	> list partition
	
	Chkdsk
	
	>chkdsk
	>chkdsk /f
	>chkdsk /f /x
	
	Review
	> Format - formats the drive
	>diskpart manage partition
	> check for bad blocks on drives
	>sfc - finds and replace lost or corrupter filse